{"id":"math240-undetermined_240-002","cid":"MATH 240","topic":"Undetermined Coefficients","subtopic":"Particular solution — constant forcing","difficulty":2,"license":"CC BY-NC-SA (Numberbender original)","instruction":"A spring with damping satisfies y'' + {a}y' + {b}y = {c} (constant forcing). Find the equilibrium (particular) solution.","params":{"a":{"type":"int","min":2,"max":8},"b":{"type":"int","min":2,"max":8},"c":{"type":"int","min":4,"max":24}},"answer_expr":"undetermined_240","steps":["At equilibrium, y'' = y' = 0. So {b}·yp = {c}.","yp = {c}/{b} = {answer_undetermined_240}."],"tags":["ode","equilibrium","spring","undetermined-coefficients"]}
